   "itemId": "10",
   "html": "<h2 class=\"headline-4 FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__featuredTitle\" _item_id=\"10\">Inviting hard questions</h2>"
  },
  {
   "itemId": "11",
   "html": "<div class=\"FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__meta\" _item_id=\"11\"><span class=\"caption bold\">Announcements</span><time class=\"FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__date caption bold\">Jul 9, 2026</time></div>"
  },
  {
   "itemId": "12",
   "html": "<p class=\"body-3 serif FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__body\" _item_id=\"12\">We’re asking the public for their hardest questions about AI, and committing to show our work as we address them.</p>"
  },
  {
   "itemId": "13",
   "html": "<div class=\"FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__meta\" _item_id=\"13\"><span class=\"caption bold\">Features</span><time class=\"FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__date caption bold\">Jul 6, 2026</time></div>"
  },
  {
   "itemId": "14",
   "html": "<h4 class=\"headline-6 FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__title\" _item_id=\"14\">The Making of Claude Code</h4>"
  },
  {
   "itemId": "15",
   "html": "<p class=\"body-3 serif FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__body\" _item_id=\"15\">The inside story of how Claude Code went from an internal CLI to Anthropic's coding agent, told by researchers, engineers and early users who built it.</p>"
  },
  {
   "itemId": "16",
   "html": "<div class=\"FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__meta\" _item_id=\"16\"><span class=\"caption bold\">Announcements</span><time class=\"FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__date caption bold\">Jun 30, 2026</time></div>"
  },
  {
   "itemId": "17",
   "html": "<h4 class=\"headline-6 FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__title\" _item_id=\"17\">Redeploying Fable 5</h4>"
  },
  {
   "itemId": "18",
   "html": "<p class=\"body-3 serif FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__body\" _item_id=\"18\">Fable 5 returns globally July 1. We're also proposing an industry-wide framework for scoring jailbreak severity, together with Amazon, Microsoft, Google, and other Glasswing partners. </p>"
  },
  {
   "itemId": "19",
   "html": "<div class=\"FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__meta\" _item_id=\"19\"><span class=\"caption bold\">Product</span><time class=\"FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__date caption bold\">Jun 30, 2026</time></div>"
  },
  {
   "itemId": "20",
   "html": "<h4 class=\"headline-6 FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__title\" _item_id=\"20\">Introducing Claude Sonnet 5</h4>"
  },
  {
   "itemId": "21",
   "html": "<p class=\"body-3 serif FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__body\" _item_id=\"21\">Sonnet 5 delivers frontier performance across coding, agents, and professional work at scale.</p>"
  },
  {
   "itemId": "22",
   "html": "<div class=\"FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__meta\" _item_id=\"22\"><span class=\"caption bold\">Announcements</span><time class=\"FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__date caption bold\">Jun 30, 2026</time></div>"
  },
  {
   "itemId": "23",
   "html": "<h4 class=\"headline-6 FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__title\" _item_id=\"23\">Claude Science, an AI workbench for scientists, is now available</h4>"
  },
  {
   "itemId": "24",
   "html": "<p class=\"body-3 serif FeaturedGrid-module-scss-module__W1FydW__body\" _item_id=\"24\">Claude Science is a customizable app that integrates the tools and packages researchers most often use, produces auditable artifacts, and provides flexible access to computing resources.</p>"
  },
